# H11's module + its golden live in dirs literally named "build" (design §5:
# helm/src/build/*.lev) — real source, not compiler/plan output. Re-include the
# dirs and their contents; the nested trident plan-output `build/` (e.g.
# tests/build/build/) is still caught by the **/build/ rule above.
!src/build/
!src/build/**
!tests/build/
!tests/build/**
# ...but re-ignore trident's plan output nested under the test project dir.
tests/build/build/
